defect-mlff
===========

Toolkit to sample and diversify defect configurations, generate VASP/FHI-aims inputs, and prepare MLFF/MACE datasets.

Install
-------
```
pip install -e .
```
This exposes CLIs:
- `defect-mlff-diversify` → sample configurations.
- `defect-mlff-generate` → write AIMs/VASP inputs.
  - `defect-mlff-generate write-aims ...`
  - `defect-mlff-generate write-vasp ...`

Quick start
-----------
- Sample configs from a JSON/YAML spec:
  ```
  defect-mlff-diversify --configs path/to/sample_config.yaml
  ```
- Write AIMs inputs from a config list (first 10 entries):
  ```
  defect-mlff-generate write-aims \
    --config outputs/.../jsons/0_V_Mo.json \
    --k 10 \
    --output-dir outputs/.../relax \
    --defaults /path/to/fhi-aims/defaults_2020
  ```
- Write VASP inputs for a single config:
  ```
  defect-mlff-generate write-vasp \
    --config outputs/.../jsons/0_V_Mo.json \
    --config-index 0 \
    --template-dir inputs/vasp \
    --output-dir outputs/.../vasp_relax
  ```
  ```
